  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<ul><li><strong>Category:</strong> Clan</li><li><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Ursari Clan</li></ul><p>Your upbringing has allowed you to bond with nature more closely than others would have the opportunity to do.</p><ul><li>Increase your Strength or Charisma score by 1, to a max of 20.</li><li>You gain proficiency in Animal Handling and Nature. If you already have proficiency in either of these, you instead gain expertise.</li><li>Beasts have a friendly disposition to you. Through sound and gestures, you can communicate simple ideas with beasts. They can understand the meaning of your words, though you have no special ability to understand them in return. You have advantage on all Wisdom or Charisma checks you make intereacting with them.</li><li>You can use your action to make an animal handling check (you may use Strength in place of Wisdom) against a hostile beast in an attempt to calm it. The DC for this check equals 15 + the beast's level. On a success, it is no longer hostile to you until it takes damage.</li></ul>",
